title: Bob Norval
text: Robert Norval was an Australian <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who played one match as a <a href="Hooker%20%28rugby%20league%29">hooker</a> for the <a href="Sydney%20Roosters">Eastern Suburbs</a> against <a href="North%20Sydney%20Bears">North Sydney</a> in 1940.
